<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>记得你是叫开司吧</b></font>

249
00:13:31,310 --> 00:13:32,020
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>是</b></font>

250
00:13:32,580 --> 00:13:36,350
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你也是和人约好了会救你才进来的吗</b></font>

251
00:13:36,490 --> 00:13:37,120
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>算是吧</b></font>

252
00:13:37,220 --> 00:13:39,420
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>那真是太好了</b></font>

253
00:13:39,520 --> 00:13:43,230
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>但是 现在这状态究竟该说是好吗</b></font>

254
00:13:43,390 --> 00:13:46,230
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我们可以离开这里的</b></font>

255
00:13:46,530 --> 00:13:48,600
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>只要能离开这里 债务就一笔勾销</b></font>

256
00:13:48,730 --> 00:13:50,230
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>可以重新来过</b></font>

257
00:13:50,630 --> 00:13:53,400
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>不用再惧怕别人追债了</b></font>

258
00:13:53,500 --> 00:13:56,610
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开司 我们可以重新来过的</b></font>

259
00:13:56,810 --> 00:13:58,410
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>可以重新来过的</b></font>

260
00:14:00,520 --> 00:14:03,310
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这一切都是拜酒井先生所赐</b></font>

261
00:14:03,610 --> 00:14:07,150
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>因为那个人给我指了一条可以活下去的明路</b></font>

262
00:14:07,610 --> 00:14:11,920
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>他说会赚六颗星星把我救上去</b></font>

263
00:14:12,760 --> 00:14:14,220
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这还很难说呢</b></font>

264
00:14:14,990 --> 00:14:18,930
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>主办方依然有可能改变计划</b></font>

265
00:14:19,260 --> 00:14:22,900
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>比如这一次不允许买卖什么的</b></font>

266
00:14:22,970 --> 00:14:24,070
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这种事情...</b></font>

267
00:14:29,670 --> 00:14:30,610
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>利根川</b></font>

268
00:14:31,370 --> 00:14:35,850
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>已经过了四小时 限定猜拳就此结束</b></font>

269
00:14:36,710 --> 00:14:38,050
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>但是 根据我的观察</b></font>

270
00:14:38,220 --> 00:14:41,890
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这个楼层里还有许多只有一颗星或两颗星的人</b></font>

271
00:14:42,690 --> 00:14:46,820
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>把这些人全都送去小黑屋我也实在于心不忍</b></font>

272
00:14:47,360 --> 00:14:50,280
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>希望尽力救出几人 尽力</b></font>

273
00:14:50,860 --> 00:14:53,400
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>所以我们在讨论后所得出的结论</b></font>

274
00:14:53,630 --> 00:14:57,530
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>就是作为特例 临时提供买卖星星的机会</b></font>

275
00:14:57,830 --> 00:15:01,040
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>通过买卖 能凑到三颗星就能得救</b></font>

276
00:15:02,770 --> 00:15:04,370
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>太好了 得救了</b></font>

277
00:15:09,080 --> 00:15:13,470
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>太好了 这样对方就可以指定要救的人了 得救了</b></font>

278
00:15:13,680 --> 00:15:17,050
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>太好了 其实我还有些不安的</b></font>

279
00:15:17,290 --> 00:15:19,960
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>担心会不会最后关头被翻盘</b></font>

280
00:15:20,890 --> 00:15:23,930
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>接下来只要等酒井先生救我就行了</b></font>

281
00:15:25,770 --> 00:15:26,400
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>怎么了</b></font>

282
00:15:28,020 --> 00:15:29,520
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你为什么要笑</b></font>

283
00:15:30,070 --> 00:15:32,840
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>抱歉 如果让你们不快了我道歉</b></font>

284
00:15:33,340 --> 00:15:36,440
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>只是实在太可笑了</b></font>

285
00:15:36,470 --> 00:15:37,210
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>可笑?</b></font>

286
00:15:38,310 --> 00:15:40,240
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>那个叫酒井的家伙在哪?</b></font>

287
00:15:41,120 --> 00:15:43,050
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>在哪...在哪是...</b></font>

288
00:15:43,680 --> 00:15:45,780
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>可能去上厕所了吧</b></font>

289
00:15:46,000 --> 00:15:48,790
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>喂喂 你究竟傻到什么程度</b></font>

290
00:15:48,990 --> 00:15:52,390
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>那个叫酒井的家伙 现在一定在喝啤酒吧</b></font>

291
00:15:52,890 --> 00:15:53,560
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>在楼上</b></font>

292
00:15:54,470 --> 00:15:55,290
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>楼上?</b></font>

293
00:15:57,330 --> 00:15:58,220
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>怎么可能...</b></font>

294
00:16:15,450 --> 00:16:20,020
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>可以最后改变计划的 也不光只是主办方嘛</b></font>

295
00:16:20,480 --> 00:16:24,320
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你刚才说你的同伴挣了六颗星星吧</b></font>

296
00:16:24,790 --> 00:16:27,420
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>那样的话本来就没法救你</b></font>

297
00:16:29,000 --> 00:16:31,040
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>酒井是第二次参赛吧</b></font>

298
00:16:31,500 --> 00:16:35,090
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>第二次参赛的人要四颗星才能活下来</b></font>

299
00:16:35,340 --> 00:16:36,050
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>四颗</b></font>

300
00:16:36,510 --> 00:16:42,640
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>他如果想救这家伙的话 必须自己出钱再买一颗星星</b></font>

301
00:16:43,140 --> 00:16:45,230
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>在这船上谁会做这种事</b></font>

302
00:16:45,980 --> 00:16:47,740
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>被人背叛是理所当然的</b></font>

303
00:16:48,380 --> 00:16:52,820
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>不过嘛 就算那个叫酒井的挣了7颗或者8颗星星</b></font>

304
00:16:52,850 --> 00:16:54,550
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>一样会抛弃他</b></font>

305
00:16:54,950 --> 00:16:57,890
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>在他看来 这家伙只是颗弃子罢了</b></font>

306
00:16:57,990 --> 00:16:59,560
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>别说了 适可而止吧</b></font>

307
00:17:01,160 --> 00:17:01,990
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>虽然在这件事上</b></font>

308
00:17:02,160 --> 00:17:03,760
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>一味听从那个叫酒井的家伙的指示</b></font>

309
00:17:03,890 --> 00:17:07,580
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>没有构筑起真正的人际关系的这个大叔也有过错</b></font>

310
00:17:07,930 --> 00:17:09,930
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>但即便如此也不该用这种口气说话</b></font>

311
00:17:10,600 --> 00:17:11,960
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>别生气嘛</b></font>

312
00:17:12,440 --> 00:17:14,270
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你叫我住口我住口就是了</b></font>

313
00:17:14,900 --> 00:17:16,870
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>对一条已死的狗多端几脚也没意义</b></font>

314
00:17:17,470 --> 00:17:20,390
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>只是 有一点我比较在意</b></font>

315
00:17:20,940 --> 00:17:24,610
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你刚才说什么真正的人际关系</b></font>

316
00:17:24,950 --> 00:17:27,380
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>什么叫真正的...</b></font>

317
00:17:29,590 --> 00:17:33,360
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>那就是...一起度过这限定猜拳中的层层困难</b></font>

318
00:17:33,460 --> 00:17:41,830
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>那个...超越了背叛与不背叛的信赖或者说羁绊...</b></font>

319
00:17:42,200 --> 00:17:43,330
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>那算什么</b></font>

320
00:17:44,930 --> 00:17:46,910
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你这小子 会死吧</b></font>

321
00:17:49,120 --> 00:17:51,370
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>如果你想让别人从这里救你出去</b></font>

322
00:17:51,830 --> 00:17:54,290
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>就像我这样带着钱进来</b></font>

323
00:17:54,790 --> 00:17:57,630
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>或者在外头藏着极具价值的宝贝</b></font>

324
00:17:58,050 --> 00:18:00,630
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>使他们不得不救你</b></font>

325
00:18:01,020 --> 00:18:06,860
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>然而你却说什么信赖羁绊之类的莫名奇妙的梦话</b></font>

326
00:18:06,890 --> 00:18:08,690
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>闭嘴 闭嘴 闭嘴</b></font>

327
00:18:09,060 --> 00:18:10,660
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你懂什么</b></font>

328
00:18:10,930 --> 00:18:13,060
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我和古畑还有安藤所跨过的</b></font>

329
00:18:13,330 --> 00:18:17,000
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>至今为止的那些地狱 所建立的羁绊 信赖</b></font>

330
00:18:17,130 --> 00:18:20,000
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>那么各位 只有十分钟时间</b></font>

331
00:18:20,640 --> 00:18:23,310
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>在这十分钟之内还没法凑到三颗星的话</b></font>

332
00:18:23,670 --> 00:18:25,240
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>就必须去小黑屋了</b></font>

333
00:18:25,530 --> 00:18:30,310
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>那个 我想用三颗星星救回小黑屋里的人</b></font>

334
00:18:31,510 --> 00:18:32,750
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>请自便</b></font>

335
00:18:33,830 --> 00:18:35,220
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>谢谢您</b></font>

336
00:18:37,350 --> 00:18:39,020
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>看到了吗 听到了吗</b></font>

337
00:18:39,260 --> 00:18:42,330
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>他们根本没想过要背叛我</b></font>

338
00:18:44,030 --> 00:18:47,060
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>原来如此 这还真是出乎意料的发展</b></font>

339
00:18:47,330 --> 00:18:49,330
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>但是 还很难说哦</b></font>

340
00:18:49,470 --> 00:18:50,330
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你还要乱吠吗</b></font>

341
00:18:53,270 --> 00:18:54,800
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>那么接下来十分钟</b></font>

342
00:18:55,610 --> 00:18:56,230
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开始</b></font>

343
00:19:03,280 --> 00:19:04,860
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>五百万 五百万</b></font>

344
00:19:06,280 --> 00:19:07,870
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>五百万卖给我吧</b></font>

345
00:19:07,990 --> 00:19:09,700
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>求你了 我出五百万</b></font>

346
00:19:10,040 --> 00:19:12,210
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>安藤 我要卖一颗</b></font>

347
00:19:12,500 --> 00:19:15,040
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>即使卖掉一颗 还能剩下三颗</b></font>

348
00:19:15,330 --> 00:19:16,750
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>可以救开司的</b></font>

349
00:19:17,590 --> 00:19:19,750
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>来 出五百万的</b></font>

350
00:19:22,220 --> 00:19:24,430
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>太好了 太好了</b></font>

351
00:19:24,770 --> 00:19:26,470
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这样我就能上二楼了</b></font>

352
00:19:27,500 --> 00:19:28,340
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>卖给我吧</b></font>

353
00:19:28,440 --> 00:19:30,010
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>闪开吧 已经没有了</b></font>

354
00:19:30,930 --> 00:19:34,230
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>剩下的三颗是为了救重要的伙伴的星星</b></font>

355
00:19:34,690 --> 00:19:35,940
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>去找别人吧</b></font>

356
00:19:36,190 --> 00:19:38,270
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>离我远点 离我远点啊</b></font>

357
00:19:38,650 --> 00:19:41,230
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>喂 叫你们走啊 走啊</b></font>

358
00:19:41,650 --> 00:19:43,240
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我已经没有多余的星星卖你们了</b></font>

359
00:19:53,160 --> 00:19:57,210
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>那个 我想救那里头的人</b></font>

360
00:19:58,420 --> 00:19:59,290
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>古畑</b></font>

361
00:20:05,630 --> 00:20:08,430
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>穿越了死亡的同伴之间的羁绊</b></font>

362
00:20:09,600 --> 00:20:12,220
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开司 终于成功生还</b></font>

363
00:20:16,790 --> 00:20:17,720
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>就是这个人</b></font>

364
00:20:18,150 --> 00:20:19,190
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我想救这...</b></font>

365
00:20:21,730 --> 00:20:24,230
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我不是说过了 没有星星卖给你们了</b></font>

366
00:20:26,830 --> 00:20:28,780
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>怎么了 安藤</b></font>

367
00:20:30,200 --> 00:20:35,370
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>不行 这些星星还有钱 我都不会放手</b></font>

368
00:20:35,830 --> 00:20:37,170
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>不想放手</b></font>

369
00:20:38,330 --> 00:20:39,630
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你在说什么</b></font>

370
00:20:40,340 --> 00:20:42,460
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>那样不是就救不了开司了</b></font>

